metadata.description:
Once upon a time, Viviane and Niels update the team on their journey around Nupic Island, how Monty has progressed and the milestones they've achieved. 

This video shows the progress in the 6 months between the first chapter of the Legend of Monty (https://youtu.be/D4iz9cH1MoA) and July 2023.

00:00 Introduction
01:32 In the Beginning There Were Principles
02:45 NuPIC Island
04:10 Evidence LM Town
05:40 Fisher Village
06:01 Castle of Compositionality
06:27 Tower of Multiple Objects
08:07 Grotto of Dynamic Environments
09:15 Hierarchical Action Policies
09:46 Future Roadmap
